#~ msgid ""
#~ "When entering a new transaction with this option, &kmymoney; will display "
#~ "a list of previous transaction for the payee and account. If previous "
#~ "transactions differ in less than X percent, they will be considered "
#~ "identical. If the percentage is 0, all previous transactions for the "
